>> title: Bolognese Bowl
>> cuisine: Italian
>> tags: bowl, quick-assembly, vegan, gluten-free, soy-free
>> servings: 1

-- Assembly time: 5 minutes

Scoop @../components/grains/jasmine-rice{1%cup} (or polenta) as base in #bowl{}.

Heat @../components/proteins/lentil-bolognese{1%cup} and add to bowl.

Top with @../components/vegetables/italian-roasted-vegetables{1/2%cup}.

Drizzle @olive oil{1%tbsp}.

Garnish with @fresh basil{2%tbsp}.

-- Italian comfort food in bowl form
